name: 100 Months After Midnight
description:
"Liminality After Midnight" shows us what our world might look like after it ends. In 2021, the "Doomsay Clock" predict  that we are 100 seconds away from a possible end of the world on a 24-hour scale. The more your close to midnight, the more you are from the end  
No one knows how il will happend, how it will end, but we all know midnight is close. Possibly a pandemic, a total war or a meteorite? These speculative images co-created with an AI model shows liminal spaces after human existed.
